entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued October 19 at 4:11PM AKDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Elevated Surf Tonight Through Friday... Elevated surf will continue tonight and cause minor beach erosion. Northwest winds to 25 to 35 mph will decrease to 15 mph late Friday afternoon. The surf will decrease Friday evening. Residents with items on the beach should move them inland to prevent them from washing away.

entry.summary: ...Periods of Snow and Blowing Snow Through Tonight...
